<subSubSection lastPageId="48" pageId="47" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1436,1618,2030]" pageId="47">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,339,1888,1914]" pageId="47">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named for my friend Benjamin Bottom to acknowledge his feline support during the preparation of this paper.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1436,1618,2030]" box="[198,1061,1965,1992]" pageId="47">
